Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.96,0:24:43.00,ED CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}今晚就讓你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.44,0:24:48.00,ED CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}無法抹去的無敵的愛
